A woman from Gichira village in Tetu constituency celebrated her 100th birthday on Sunday. Elizabeth Wamaitha said she is happy to be alive. She said the secret to long life is eating healthy food and praying. &ldquo;She has a very sharp memory. It&rsquo;s like a memory card has been put in her brain,&rdquo; grandson Waruru Ndegwa said. Wamaitha&rsquo;s daughter Gladys, 51, said her mother likes singing.